---
title: Loaded Pork & Roast Veggie Fajita Bowl with Garlic Brown Rice & Cheddar Cheese
description: Roast veggies and pork is a taste sensation for hungry mouths. Spiced pork cooks to tender perfection when cut up into strips
and the charred smokey corn is simply irresistible when partnered with a variety of roast veggies. Make sure to soak up all those
flavours with a serving of brown rice with bursts of fragrant garlic.

